  "about_item": [
    "🛡️ Anxiety Calming & Female Spay Recovery (Potty Friendly): Applies gentle, wrap-style pressure to help calm anxious pets. For female spay recovery, the Body Module can be used alone to cover the chest and belly, while the open-rear design allows normal potty breaks. A flexible alternative to fully enclosed recovery suits. Not intended for male neuter",
    "🤫 Silent Self-Gripping Fabric (No Velcro Noise): No ripping sounds, no startling. The quiet self-gripping fabric allows silent, fully adjustable wrapping and removal, making it especially suitable for dogs and cats that are anxious or in recovery, as pets tend to be more sensitive during stressful or healing periods",
    "📏 UNIVERSAL CUSTOM FIT (Patent Pending): The 2-piece structure allows independent adjustment of chest, neck, and back length for a secure, custom fit. Designed to fit standard body types while adapting to long bodies (Corgis) or broad chests (Bulldogs). Modules can also be used independently—see A+ for modular use cases",
    "🤝 Dual Calming Support: Wrap Pressure + Familiar Scent: Wrap-style pressure combined with familiar scent comfort helps reduce stress during separation, recovery, or travel. Modules can be briefly worn or handled by the owner before use, allowing familiar scent to remain and provide added reassurance",
    "🛋️ Fur Barrier & Easy Care: Helps collect loose fur to reduce shedding on furniture. If adhesion weakens due to fur buildup, simply clean the surface with a lint roller to restore grip. Machine washable for easy everyday care"
  ],
