        "title": "Awesome thunder shirt for cats!",
        "text": "Excellent product! I bought this for my cat whose stress grooms. It’s really nice. I love the fabric, it doesn’t need to be pulled over the head so even putting it on them is low stress. So far our cat doesn’t seem to mind it either. I’m going to order more",
