      {
        "position": 2,
        "title": "flexible, comfortable, and silent to remove. excellent for cats!",
        "text": "this thing is amazing! our cat was meowing loudly and excessively for almost 2 years since we adopted him. by chance we figured out that putting this \"Kitty holster\" harness on him calmed him way down (we realized he had anxiety.. duh!) and he started acting like a normal cat and would only meow occasionally! our problem was finally solved, however it was a bit stiff and restrictive and he didn't seem totally comfortable; he couldn't jump up on his cat tree very well. I knew about the thundershirt and thought about getting one, but then I saw this, and I'm so glad I did! it has the exact same calming effect on him and it's way more flexible and comfortable. it is also way easier to take off...the kitty holster has strong Velcro because it's made so that you can take them on walks. I had a thundershirt for my dog and remember that it had velcro too. Forest was trying to bite us when we took it off because it made a lot of noise and scared him. no noise with this one! I'm so glad I took a chance on this because it didn't have a lot of reviews, but the ones it did have were glowing. I am now joining that crowd and plan to tell everyone I know who has a cat!",
        "rating": 5,
