      {
        "position": 4,
        "title": "Amazing Calming Jacket — Noticeable Anxiety Relief & Comfortable Fit",
        "text": "I bought this for my anxious pup and wow — it’s been a game-changer! Unlike other calming wraps I’ve tried, the modular 2-piece design with a detachable ear hood makes it really versatile. The vest feels snug without restricting movement, and my dog seems much calmer during thunderstorms and fireworks. The silent self-adhesive fabric is easy to adjust and stays in place — no noisy Velcro ripping off mid-walk! The ear hood is a bonus during loud events, and surprisingly she doesn’t fuss about wearing it. It’s helped with separation stress and even eased her reactions on car rides.Highly recommend to anyone with a nervous dog or cat! 🐾",
