        "text": "Let me start with the very nice fabric -I guess I don't have to understand how Velcroless fabrics works -but it does ! It sticks to itself and does so silently ....I assume the silence is to not alarm an already alarmed dog that ur trying to keep calm-very good idea ! The material is reversible and works identically on either side ..it is also fully washable ...(100% poly .. )My pictures are of my 80 pound pit bull -she shakes with thunder ..she was very comfortable with the vest on (wore it for about 30 minutes for my pictures ) -and I've yet to test it during storm -but I will next storm and come back here to edit this review with an update of how it worked \"under fire\" ...but so far I couldn't ask for anything more for my very fair $35 price ..",
