        "title": "Very light, no sounds when applying/removing, didn’t notice a difference in comfort for our dog",
        "text": "We ordered this for use with our mini dachshund how shakes like crazy on car rides. It fit her body well, is very soft and super easy to put on and take off. The way it attaches to itself is great! Sticks in any position and doesn’t make a Velcro type sound when removing it. It’s hard to explain but it’s a smooth process to put on and take off, no noise which is great because our dachshund flinches at pretty much any sound she’s not familiar with. It seems like decent quality and should be fairly durable in the long term. Unfortunately we didn’t see any noticeable improvement with her shaking in the car. We were really hopeful it would bring her comfort. Obviously every animal is different so you may have a different experience then us. If you’re like most people you’d try anything to make your “baby” happy. Best of luck if you decide to purchase and try this out!",
